S, No . 8 (I)
MOST IMM
No.1/34/1/2012-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 19th March, 2012
The undersigned is directed to say that Shri Dinesh Trivedi relinquished the
charge of the office of the Minister of Railways with effect from the 19th March, 2012.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman and Members of the Planning
Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:-
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
Copy also forwarded for information to :-
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/ Additional Secretaries to the
Govt. of India/Chairman, Railway Board/Accounts Officer, Pay & Accounts Office, Cabinet
Affairs, for information.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the Govt. of India/Lok Sabha
Secretariat (Distribution Branch)/Rajya Sabha Secretariat (Distribution Branch)/ Establishment
Officer, Department of Personnel & Training/Ministry of External Affairs (Protocol
Division)/Press Information Bureau/Section Officer, NGO Section, Prime Minister's Office.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
*ANV*
425 Copies.
